com.estimote.coresdk.recognition.packets

Class Nearable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.estimote.coresdk.recognition.packets.Packet
      • com.estimote.coresdk.recognition.packets.Nearable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Nearable
extends Packet
    Immutable representation of a nearable.

    Two Nearables are considered equal if their identifiers are equal.

    You can find nearby Nearables using BeaconManager.startNearableDiscovery() method.
